<li id="cite_note-JUGGLING_WORK-14"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-JUGGLING_WORK_14-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-JUGGLING_WORK_14-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-JUGGLING_WORK_14-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text"><span class="citation Journal">Landsman, Paige (1994). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.lexisnexis.com/hottopics/lnacademic/?shr=t&csi=6935&sr=HLEAD(Juggling+work+and+family)+and+date+is+August,%201994">"JUGGLING WORK AND FAMILY FLEXIBLE SCHEDULING, AND CHANGING ATTITUDES HELP BALANCE DEMANDS."</a>. <i>Business Insurance</i>: 16<span class="printonly">. <a rel="nofollow" class="external free" href="http://www.lexisnexis.com/hottopics/lnacademic/?shr=t&csi=6935&sr=HLEAD(Juggling+work+and+family)+and+date+is+August,%201994">http://www.lexisnexis.com/hottopics/lnacademic/?shr=t&amp;csi=6935&amp;sr=HLEAD(Juggling+work+and+family)+and+date+is+August,%201994</a></span>.</span></span></li>
